JOHANNESBURG - Delegates arrived in their numbers and dressed in their finery for the ANC's 54th Elective Conference on Saturday.  Although the official programme started hours later than scheduled, spirits appeared high as delegates sang and danced waiting for the speeches to begin.    Photos above: Delegates arrive at Nasrec on Saturday for the ANC conference. Reuters / Rogan Ward / Siphiwe Sibeko. Photos below: eNCA.     eNCA